nt-family=\"sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#333\">O</text><text x=\"292\" y=\"156.0\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#333\">x</text><text x=\"164.0\" y=\"26\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#333\">y</text><line x1=\"30.0\" y1=\"-248.6\" x2=\"290.0\" y2=\"271.4\" stroke=\"#1565c0\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"261.4\" y=\"228.3\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1565c0\">2x + y = 8</text><line x1=\"30.0\" y1=\"308.6\" x2=\"290.0\" y2=\"48.6\" stroke=\"#c62828\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"261.4\" y=\"61.1\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#c62828\">x - y = 1</text><circle cx=\"215.7\" cy=\"122.9\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#000\"/></svg></figure></p>",
  "stem": "<p>The graph above shows a system of two linear equations in the xy-plane. Which of the following systems of equations has the same solution as the system shown in the graph?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>2x + y = 8 and x + y = 1</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p>4x + 2y = 16 and 2x &minus; 2y = 2</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "c",
      "content": "<p>2x + y = 16 and x &minus; y = 1</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "d",
      "content": "<p>4x + 2y = 16 and x &minus; y = 2</p>"
    }
